<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The suburb's elevation sets it apart from the flat inner north. Properties on the ridge streets benefit from views that are unusual at this price point and distance from the city, and the suburb's topography creates a natural sense of separation from the arterial road network that makes the residential streets genuinely quiet. Wavell State High School draws families from across the inner north-east, and the school catchment is a direct factor in buyer decision-making for a significant proportion of the homes sold here.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Gympie Road to the east provides bus access to the CBD and connects quickly to the rail network at Nundah. Nundah's retail strip and its rail connection are within easy reach, and Clayfield's café and dining amenity is accessible without living at Clayfield prices. The housing stock reflects decades of family ownership: solid post-war homes, renovated family residences and the occasional character home, with the best properties consistently sitting on the quieter ridge streets where the views and the peace are both at their best.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Wavell Heights Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Inner North-East Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Elevated Family Living</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Strong schools, consistent growth</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/nundah" style="color:#c4912a;">Nundah</a>, <a href="/suburbs/clayfield" style="color:#c4912a;">Clayfield</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kedron" style="color:#c4912a;">Kedron</a>, <a href="/suburbs/wooloowin" style="color:#c4912a;">Wooloowin</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

